This folder intentionally has no bundled SCImago CSV.

The build spec (pubmed_tool_spec.md §2) calls for bundling a default
`scimagojr_2025.csv` here, copied from `../database/scimagojr_2025.csv`.
That source file does not exist anywhere in this environment, so no
default dataset ships with the app.

The app works fine with this folder empty: journal-tier badges show
"—" (not indexed) for every result until a user uploads a real SCImago
CSV via Settings -> "Upload SCImago CSV" (see index.html / app.js
handleCsvUpload). Once uploaded, the parsed data is cached in the
browser's IndexedDB, not written back to this folder.
